can't both be satisfied at once.  Let's plug our answers back into the
original system of equations to see how well they match.

     2:  [-11.64, 14.08, -3.64]     1:  [5.6, 2., 3., 11.2]
     1:  [ [ 1, 2, 3 ]                  .
           [ 4, 5, 6 ]
           [ 7, 6, 0 ]
           [ 2, 4, 6 ] ]
         .

         r 7                            <TAB> *

