     3:  3               4:  3           3:  3       2:  3      1:  -6
     2:  3               3:  3           2:  3       1:  9          .
     1:  2               2:  3           1:  3           .
         .               1:  2               .
                             .

      M-<TAB> M-<TAB>     <TAB> <RET> M-<TAB>         z s          *          -

     1:  -6                          2:  4          1:  11      2:  11
         .                           1:  2              .       1:  11
